nt is expelling oxygen. This should, in theory, improve the air quality.<\/p>\n","answer_id":41220,"question_id":41198,"up_vote_count":2}],"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/questions/41198/how-do-house-plants-affect-the-quality-of-air-in-a-house","last_activity_date":1449195624,"creation_date":1449157205,"answer_count":1,"title":"How do house plants affect the quality of air in a house?","body":"<p>Do house plants affect the air in the house by taking it from the rooms and it is put in the dirt to make it moist then we have no air.<\/p>\n","question_id":41198,"tags":["botany"],"score":-1,"down_vote_count":2,"closed_reason":"unclear what you're asking","is_answered":true,"view_count":83,"up_vote_count":1,"last_edit_date":1449195624},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/fe87113ced5f370d038b90a43fd1fe1f?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":408,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/408/anixx","reputation":909,"display_name":"Anixx","accept_rate":20},"answers":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://i.stack.imgur.com/F4aa0.jpg?s=128&g=1","user_type":"registered","user_id":6380,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/6380/bunk","reputation":873,"display_name":"Bunk"},"score":9,"is_accepted":false,"comments":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/fe87113ced5f370d038b90a43fd1fe1f?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":408,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/408/anixx","reputation":909,"display_name":"Anixx","accept_rate":20},"score":1,"post_id":17058,"edited":false,"creation_date":1398953279,"comment_id":23080,"body":"I doubt it falls off, the sources I looked up say that the whole yolk sac goes inside the bird&#39;s body."},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://i.stack.imgur.com/F4aa0.jpg?s=128&g=1","user_type":"registered","user_id":6380,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/6380/bunk","reputation":873,"display_name":"Bunk"},"score":0,"post_id":17058,"r